Reviews

review by - Yelp

Deborah B:

This gem is a great addition to Johns Island. The staff is courteous, efficient and friendly. The food is outstanding and there are a variety of options for cocktails. The atmosphere is perfect for every member of the family to enjoy from the televisions with sports to the amusements for both adults and children. The Natural is definitely a great experience for locals and guests.
